trait-blindness-name = Blindness
trait-blindness-desc = You can't see clearly past a few meters in front of you.

trait-poor-vision-name = Short-sighted
trait-poor-vision-desc = Your vision is significantly inhibited beyond a short-ish range without corrective glasses.

trait-narcolepsy-name = Narcoleptic
trait-narcolepsy-desc = You fall into a light sleep seemingly at random.

trait-pacifist-name = Pacifist
trait-pacifist-desc = You cannot attack or hurt any living beings. Does not prevent actions that aren't strictly hostile.

permanent-blindness-trait-examined = [color=lightblue]{CAPITALIZE(POSS-ADJ($target))} eyes are glassy and unfocused. It doesn't seem like {SUBJECT($target)} can see you well, if at all.[/color]

trait-lightweight-name = Lightweight drunk
trait-lightweight-desc = Alcohol has a stronger effect on you.

trait-monochromacy-name = Monochromacy
trait-monochromacy-desc = You are fully colorblind and can't see color.

trait-muted-name = Mute
trait-muted-desc = You can't speak out loud. Prevents you from using Shouts.

trait-paracusia-name = Paracusia
trait-paracusia-desc = You hear sounds that aren't really there.

trait-unrevivable-name = Unrevivable
trait-unrevivable-desc = You are unable to be revived without magic or the round restarting. The character is of course not deleted and can be selected again.

trait-pirate-accent-name = Pirate accent
trait-pirate-accent-desc = Yarrr, matey!

trait-accentless-name = Accentless
trait-accentless-desc = You don't have the accent that your species would usually have.

trait-frontal-lisp-name = Frontal lisp
trait-frontal-lisp-desc = You thpeak with a lithp.

trait-socialanxiety-name = Stutter
trait-socialanxiety-desc = You s-speak with a-a stut-stutter...

trait-southern-name = Southern drawl
trait-southern-desc = Ya got a different way of speakin'.

trait-snoring-name = Snoring
trait-snoring-desc = You will snore while sleeping.

trait-liar-name = Pathological liar
trait-liar-desc = You can hardly bring yourself to tell the truth. Sometimes you lie anyway.

trait-cowboy-name = Cowboy accent
trait-cowboy-desc = You speak with a distinct cowboy accent!

trait-german-name = German accent
trait-german-desc = You seem to come from space Germany.

trait-italian-name = Italian accent
trait-italian-desc = Mamma mia! You seem to have lived in critter Italy!

trait-french-name = French accent
trait-french-desc = Your accent seems to have a certain «je ne sais quoi».

trait-spanish-name = Spanish accent
trait-spanish-desc = Hola señor, donde esta la biblioteca.

trait-painnumbness-name = Numb
trait-painnumbness-desc = You lack any sense of feeling pain, and can't tell very accurately how hurt you are.

trait-hemophilia-name = Hemophilia
trait-hemophilia-desc = You don't stop bleeding by yourself.

trait-impaired-mobility-name = Impaired Mobility
trait-impaired-mobility-desc = You have difficulty moving without a mobility aid.

## 🌟Starlight🌟
trait-clumsy-name = Clumsy
trait-clumsy-desc = You sometimes trip over nothing.
